description:
For campsite exploring and recess adventures. With a UPF rating of 50+ the Sunnyday joggers are ready for fun in the sun.The lightweight fabric is treated to repel water and resist dirt, keeping kids looking cleaner longer.Lightweight nylon feels cool against the skin and dries quickly.DWR finish helps these joggers brush off dust from the trail and shed light rain.UPF 50+ blocks UV during long days under the sun.Reinforced knees are ready for vigorous playground sessions.Elasticised waistband and cuffs add a little retro style and make these pants easy to get into.Name label on the inside helps make those games of “whose is whose” a bit easier.Regular fit.

        Sustainability






